nagios-api

This is a simple REST interface to Nagios.  Run this on your Nagios host and
then sit back and enjoy a much easier, more straightforward way to accomplish
things with Nagios.

Usage is pretty easy:

    ./nagios-api -p 8080 -c /var/lib/nagios3/rw/nagios.cmd \
        -s /var/cache/nagios3/status.dat

